(1, 'Mind.Body.Soul', 'G. Sumdany Don and Savina Shah', '17880f7ee08b8831b355c8b61fd9f26f.png', '<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="line-height: 1.84615;">Had a tough week? Down on your luck? is life getting hectic? For the first time in Bangladesh, Lighthouse Bangladesh presents you with a unique workshop, conducted by G. Sumdany Don and Savina Shah, where they combine yoga and motivational training to help you achieve a metaphysical level of inspiration and a more motivated lifestyle. Forget the world for one day and come de-stress, unwind, and let us help you unleash your true potential.&nbsp;</span></div>', '<p>The interactive workshop will be broken down into six parts. The parts have been developed to both relax and inspire.&nbsp;<br><span style="letter-spacing: 0.1px; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 1.846153846; font-weight: bold;"><br></span></p><p><span style="letter-spacing: 0.1px; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 1.846153846; font-weight: bold;">1.</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.1px; text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 9.3333330154419px; line-height: normal;">&nbsp;</span><b style="letter-spacing: 0.1px; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 1.846153846;">Morning\nIce- breaker &amp; Introductions :</b></p><p class="Body" style="margin-left:9.0pt;text-indent:-9.0pt;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo2;\ntab-stops:list 9.0pt"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:\nHelvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\nposition:relative;top:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt">&nbsp; &nbsp;•<span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 9.3333330154419px; line-height: normal;">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>The\nharmony game<span style="mso-fareast-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:\nHelvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;position:relative;top:1.0pt;\nmso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="Body" style="margin-left:9.0pt;text-indent:-9.0pt;mso-list:l8 level1 lfo3;\ntab-stops:list 9.0pt"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:\nHelvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\nposition:relative;top:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">&nbsp; &nbsp;•<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Cardio\nExercise techniques to kick-start your day</p><p class="Body" style="margin-left:9.0pt;text-indent:-9.0pt;mso-list:l8 level1 lfo3;\ntab-stops:list 9.0pt"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.1px; text-indent: -9pt; line-height: 1.846153846; position: relative; top: 1pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp;•<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.1px; text-indent: -9pt; line-height: 1.846153846;">Breathing\nexercise and techniques to recharge yourself and prepare for the whole day</span></p><p class="Body"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class="Body">2. <b>Happiness and Positive Thinking<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class="Body" style="margin-left:.25in;text-indent:-9.0pt;mso-list:l9 level2 lfo5;\ntab-stops:list .25in"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:\nHelvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\nposition:relative;top:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt">•<span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 9.3333330154419px; line-height: normal;">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>Happiness\nis my right<span style="mso-fareast-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:\nHelvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;position:relative;top:1.0pt;\nmso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="Body" style="margin-left:.25in;text-indent:-9.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo6;\ntab-stops:list .25in"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:\nHelvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\nposition:relative;top:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">•<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->The\nthree picture game<span style="mso-fareast-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:\nHelvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;position:relative;top:1.0pt;\nmso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="Body" style="margin-left:.25in;text-indent:-9.0pt;mso-list:l6 level2 lfo7;\ntab-stops:list .25in"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:\nHelvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\nposition:relative;top:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">•<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->The\noptimist vs. the pessimist game<span style="mso-fareast-font-family:Helvetica;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;position:relative;\ntop:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="Body" style="margin-left:.25in;text-indent:-9.0pt;mso-list:l21 level2 lfo8;\ntab-stops:list .25in"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:\nHelvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\nposition:relative;top:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">•<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Happiness\nis the key to good health, not the other way round - yoga, the power of\npositive and calm mind<span style="mso-fareast-font-family:Helvetica;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;position:relative;\ntop:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="Body"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class="Body"><span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp;</span>3. <b>The Puzzle Vs.\nPlayer<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class="Body" style="margin-left:.25in;text-indent:-9.0pt;mso-list:l4 level2 lfo9;\ntab-stops:list .25in"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:\nHelvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\nposition:relative;top:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">•<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->I\nam my own creator - don''t be a victim, be a player!<span style="mso-fareast-font-family:\nHelvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\nposition:relative;top:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="Body" style="margin-left:.25in;text-indent:-9.0pt;mso-list:l11 level2 lfo10;\ntab-stops:list .25in"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:\nHelvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\nposition:relative;top:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">•<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Stop\ngiving excuses - take responsibility for your actions, stop the blame game and\nbe a winner!<span style="mso-fareast-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:\nHelvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;position:relative;top:1.0pt;\nmso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="Body" style="margin-left:.25in;text-indent:-9.0pt;mso-list:l13 level2 lfo11;\ntab-stops:list .25in"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:\nHelvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\nposition:relative;top:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">•<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->The\npuzzle vs. player exercise<span style="mso-fareast-font-family:Helvetica;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;position:relative;\ntop:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="Body"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class="Body">4. <b>Lunch: <o:p></o:p></b></p><p class="Body" style="margin-left:9.0pt;text-indent:-9.0pt;mso-list:l10 level1 lfo12;\ntab-stops:list 9.0pt"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:\nHelvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\nposition:relative;top:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">&nbsp; &nbsp;•<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Special\nlunch and teaching on what is the proper form of a diet for a healthy, and productive\nlifestyle<span style="mso-fareast-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:\nHelvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;position:relative;top:1.0pt;\nmso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="Body" style="margin-left:9.0pt;text-indent:-9.0pt;mso-list:l19 level1 lfo13;\ntab-stops:list 9.0pt"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:\nHelvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\nposition:relative;top:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">&nbsp; &nbsp;•<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Three\nbasic facts about nutrition for your wellbeing<span style="mso-fareast-font-family:\nHelvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\nposition:relative;top:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="Body"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class="Body"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class="Body">5. <b>The Circle of Concern vs. The Circle of Influence<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class="Body" style="margin-left:.25in;text-indent:-9.0pt;mso-list:l20 level2 lfo14;\ntab-stops:list .25in"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:\nHelvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\nposition:relative;top:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">•<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Self\nempowerment - are we focusing on things we can control and change?<span style="mso-fareast-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;position:relative;top:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="Body" style="margin-left:.25in;text-indent:-9.0pt;mso-list:l1 level2 lfo15;\ntab-stops:list .25in"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:\nHelvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\nposition:relative;top:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">•<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Positive\nPerspective = Positive Life<span style="mso-fareast-font-family:Helvetica;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;position:relative;\ntop:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="Body" style="margin-left:.25in;text-indent:-9.0pt;mso-list:l12 level2 lfo16;\ntab-stops:list .25in"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:\nHelvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\nposition:relative;top:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">•<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->How\nto manage stress? - theory and exercises<span style="mso-fareast-font-family:\nHelvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\nposition:relative;top:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="Body" style="margin-left:.25in;text-indent:-9.0pt;mso-list:l14 level2 lfo17;\ntab-stops:list .25in"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:\nHelvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\nposition:relative;top:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">•<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Deep\nbreathing exercises to reduce anxiety, stress, anger etc.<span style="mso-fareast-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;position:relative;top:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="Body"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class="Body">6. <b>The Mind<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class="Body" style="margin-left:9.0pt;text-indent:-9.0pt;mso-list:l5 level1 lfo18;\ntab-stops:list 9.0pt"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:\nHelvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\nposition:relative;top:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">&nbsp; &nbsp;•<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->The\nConscious ss. the subconscious mind<span style="mso-fareast-font-family:Helvetica;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;position:relative;\ntop:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="Body" style="margin-left:9.0pt;text-indent:-9.0pt;mso-list:l17 level1 lfo19;\ntab-stops:list 9.0pt"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:\nHelvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\nposition:relative;top:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">&nbsp; &nbsp;•<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->How\nto tap into the subconscious mind - theta healing<span style="mso-fareast-font-family:\nHelvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\nposition:relative;top:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="Body" style="margin-left:9.0pt;text-indent:-9.0pt;mso-list:l15 level1 lfo20;\ntab-stops:list 9.0pt"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:\nHelvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\nposition:relative;top:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">&nbsp; &nbsp;•<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->How\n10 minutes of your time can help change your life<span style="mso-fareast-font-family:\nHelvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\nposition:relative;top:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="Body" style="margin-left:9.0pt;text-indent:-9.0pt;mso-list:l16 level1 lfo21;\ntab-stops:list 9.0pt"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:\nHelvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\nposition:relative;top:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">&nbsp; &nbsp;•<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->The\ntremendous capacity of human beings - unleash your true potential<span style="mso-fareast-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;position:relative;top:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="Body" style="margin-left:9.0pt;text-indent:-9.0pt;mso-list:l18 level1 lfo22;\ntab-stops:list 9.0pt"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="mso-fareast-font-family:\nHelvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:Helvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;\nposition:relative;top:1.0pt;mso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">&nbsp; &nbsp;•<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->The\nfour chair game<span style="mso-fareast-font-family:Helvetica;mso-hansi-font-family:\nHelvetica;mso-bidi-font-family:Helvetica;position:relative;top:1.0pt;\nmso-text-raise:-1.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="Body"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class="Body"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p><span style="letter-spacing: 0.1px; line-height: 1.846153846;">The workshop comes with certificates, simple stationary and two\nother snack breaks.</span></p><p class="Body"><o:p></o:p></p>', '21 Aug,15', '21 Aug,15', '10:00 am', '6:00 pm', 'Lighthouse Bangladesh, 41 Kemal Ataturk Avenue, 4th floor, Banani, Dhaka', '3000 BDT/person', '<p>You can BKash us the money at 01814850661</p><p>or</p><p>deposit the amount beforehand at the following account:</p><p>Prime Bank Ltd&nbsp;</p><p><span style="letter-spacing: 0.1px; line-height: 1.846153846;">Account name: Lighthouse Bangladesh</span></p><p>A/C no: 13211030031443, Banani branch<br></p><p>and then mail us a picture or a scanned copy of that transaction receipt provided by the Bank.<span style="letter-spacing: 0.1px; line-height: 1.846153846;">.</span></p>', 'G Sumdany Don &amp; Savina Shah''s Profile', 'af3a46121e319fc477c152ca6d6de92a.pdf', NULL, '1'),
(2, 'Business 101', 'Lighthouse Bangladesh', '696f64ea9b0e4707117241cc875fce51.jpg', '<p style="text-align: justify; ">Bangladesh is now home to a growing startup scene. We are recognized as one of the most entrepreneurial countries in this world. From Teknaf to Tetulia, Tokyo to San-Francisco, our people are increasingly creating a global presence. Lighthouse Bangladesh presents "Business 101", an interactive workshop, to help entrepreneurs and soon-to-be entrepreneurs establish their presence. Come dock at the shores of Lighthouse Bangladesh and learn how to effectively start your business. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>', '<div style="text-align: justify; "><span style="line-height: 1.846153846;">Bangladesh is now home to a growing startup scene. We are recognized as one of the most entrepreneurial countries in this world. From Teknaf to Tetulia, Tokyo to San-Francisco, our people are increasingly creating a global presence. Lighthouse Bangladesh presents "Business 101", an interactive workshop, to help entrepreneurs and soon-to-be entrepreneurs establish their presence. Come dock at the shares of Lighthouse Bangladesh and learn how to effectively start your business.&nbsp;</span></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div><div><br></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div>This workshop will lead participants through all the steps necessary to go from "idea generation" to "opening day".­­­</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div><br></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div><span style="font-weight: bold;">Participants will:</span></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div><span style="font-weight: bold;"><br></span></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div><span style="font-weight: bold;">1. Learn how to do an accurate feasibility study of their idea to see if the idea has a chance of succeeding.</span></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div><span style="font-weight: bold;"><br></span></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div><span style="font-weight: bold;">2. Explore the characteristics of an entrepreneur, to discover if self-employment really is for them.</span></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div><span style="font-weight: bold;"><br></span></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div><span style="font-weight: bold;">3. Take a look at what they want from a business: financially, personally and emotionally.</span></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div><br></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div>Then participants will learn how to gather the information for their business plan, and how to put it all together.</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div><br></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div>There will be five sessions. Each session will be approximately an hour long with a presentation, a speech from our one of our guest speakers, and an exercise.&nbsp;</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div><br></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div><span style="font-weight: bold;">Topics include:</span></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div><span style="font-weight: bold;"><br></span></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div><span style="font-weight: bold;">Strategic Management:</span> This will cover the core aspects of the first steps any new business owner has to take before launching their business. This part will help the audience to structure their ideas. The first topic of discussion will be developing the value proposition. The most important thing the business has to do is solve a problem. Finding the solution to this problem will help the business owner gain a better understanding of what exactly his/her business is doing and the direction it is heading towards. Another topic will be mission, and vision; the basics of creating the mission, and vision statement, the importance of knowing what to focus on, and how your mission, and vision should define your goals and objectives. Lastly we will talk about culture, and values.</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div><br></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div><span style="font-weight: bold;">Business plan and Legal Aspects:</span> This section will cover everything an entrepreneur should have on their company''s business plan from mission, and vision statement, to SWOT, and Porter''s, to financial projections, etc. We will then talk about the legal aspects of starting one''s own business, the documents you need, what you have to pay for, and sign, etc.</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div><br></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div><span style="font-weight: bold;">Financials and fundraising: </span>In this section we will talk about how to do a preliminary financial projection for your new company. The three financial statements you will need, the basic financial projection methods, etc. Another important aspect is the different avenues through which company can raise money, and build a healthy financial model. Topics covered include: Personal budget, cost analysis, pricing method, personal investment, start-up costs, cash flow, projected income statement, etc.</div>\n\n\n\n\n<div><br></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div><span style="font-weight: bold;">Product development, marketing, and sales:</span> The first topic on this discussion will be about the different cycles of product development and what you should hope to achieve on each part. Then we will move on to talk about marketing, and sales and how to effectively do it; gathering data, and doing your research, using that research to penetrate your target market, etc.</div>\n\n\n<div><br></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div><span style="font-weight: bold;">HR, and operations, and new business tips:</span> In this section we will cover the basics of HR, operations,and corporate governance; Operational methods, how to make the organogram, SOPs, action plan, etc. In this section we will talk discuss few valuable things such as keeping costs and overheads low, the culture that should exist, the interview process, etc.</div>\n\n\n\n\n</div>', '29 Aug,15', '29 Aug,15', '12.00 pm', '5.00 pm', 'Lighthouse Bangladesh, 4th floor, 41 Kemal Ataturk Avenue, Dhaka', '500 BDT', '<p style="outline: none; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif, Arial; letter-spacing: -0.2px; color: rgb(46, 46, 46); font-size: 11.8999996185303px;">You can pay the registration fee to our Bkash number and then give us a