(3, 'Effective Communication Skills for RMG Professionals ', 'Mr. Moinuddin Chowdhury', 'b7f3b5eb21eb7bda73509136f1487b16.jpg', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;">Business\nis all about communication. So is the survival of individual’s position in the\nsociety. For RMG sector it’s more important for someone to have a very good\ncommand over communication process since the people of this industry are more\nprone to interact with the buyers. The more effectively you communicate, the\nmore widely you get connected with the world. In order to get connected with\nthe proper network and flow, you must have the effective communication skills.\nIt increases our efficiency and saves time, money, energy and efforts. The\nsecret of success in life lies in how effectively we can communicate with the\nworld around us. This program will help participants to understand how to\ncommunicate effectively at work and in business to bring productivity at work\nand even in personal life. Participating in this workshop, participants will be\nable to communicate with the clients more efficiently.<span style="line-height: 99%; font-size: 16pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;</span><span style="line-height: 99%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Garamond, serif;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Learning Outcomes:</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;">&nbsp;<span style="letter-spacing: 0.1px; line-height: 1.84615;">After successful completion of the training, the\nparticipants will be able to:</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;"><o:p></o:p></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul style="margin-top:0in" type="disc">\n <li class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;">Understand the importance of effective communication<o:p></o:p></li>\n <li class="MsoNormal